On Thursday=E2=80=99s quarterly earnings call, Bob Iger celebrated a hard-e=
arned milestone: Disney=E2=80=99s streaming business, which has been bleedi=
ng money since its inception=E2=80=94it lost $2.61 billion in 2023 alone=E2=
=80=94is finally turning a profit. Investors rewarded Disney by sending sha=
res up 16 percent for the week. It was, as my partner Matt Belloni wrote ( =
